;;; Chapter 12 presents complete extended programs.  Each section
;;; defines one algorithm and tests it.
;;; Sections tested here: 12.1 (matrix mul), 12.2 (sort/merge),
;;; 12.3 (set-of), 12.6 (printf), 12.7 (meta-circular interpreter),
;;; 12.8 (abstract objects), 12.10 (unification).
;;; Sections not directly testable in log format:
;;;   12.4 (word frequency: requires file I/O)
;;;   12.5 (Scheme printer: defines write/display -- tested via
