;;; 12.11  Multitasking with Engines
;;; ============================================================

;;; §12.11 implements engines via continuations + timer interrupts.
;;; make-engine requires SIGALRM or equivalent for tick-based preemption;
;;; not implementable in pyscheme's Python runtime.
